      "ety": "[OE. sli<?/t, sleght, probably from OD. slicht, slecht, simple, plain, D. slecht; akin to OFries. sliucht, G. schlecht, schlicht, OHG. sleht smooth, simple, Icel. sl<?/ttr smooth, Sw. slät, Goth. slahts; or uncertain origin.]",
